  "subcmds_check": {
    "_intro": "nexus check — multi-domain mathematical/physical/cognitive verification. 분야 옵션 다중 OR + 분야 내 세부 옵션. 재귀 spec n6/docs/meta_atlas_recursive.md 준수 (Level 0 atlas.n6 witness, Level 1 meta_atlas.n6 메타엔트리). 3-tier: core(engine/nexus_cli.hexa) ← module(tool/check_*.hexa) ← ai-native doc(docs/nexus_check.ai.md).",
